Step-by-step toolchain setup and build:

1) Install devkitPro (includes devkitARM and pacman):
   https://devkitpro.org/wiki/Getting_Started

2) Install 3DS toolchain packages (from the devkitPro MSYS2 shell):
   pacman -Syu
   pacman -S 3ds-dev
   pacman -S 3dstools

3) Ensure your environment has DEVKITARM set (the devkitPro installer sets this):
   echo $DEVKITARM

4) Verify bannertool and makerom are available (required for CIA builds):
   bannertool --version
   makerom -h

5) Build from this folder:
   make
   This produces a .3dsx.

6) Build a CIA (uses banner assets in src/platforms/3ds/banner):
   make cia
